---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Inicio" description="Centro Sociocultural Zaidín — Asociación vecinal en el barrio del Zaidín, Granada. 45 años impulsando igualdad, integración y participación comunitaria.">
  <!-- ==============================
       Hero
       ============================== -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-bg"></div>
    <div class="hero-content">
      <div class="hero-badge">Asociación vecinal · Granada · 1977</div>
      <h1>Centro Sociocultural Zaidín</h1>
      <p class="hero-tagline">Igualdad · Integración · Participación</p>
      <div class="hero-quote">
        <p>"La cultura popular tiene por misión, despertar la sabiduría que tiene todo hombre y mujer dentro de sí y ponerla en acción, para transformar la realidad."</p>
        <cite>— Paulo Freire</cite>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a href="/conocenos/" class="btn btn-hero-primary">Conócenos</a>
        <a href="/apoyo-a-la-regularizacion/" class="btn btn-hero-secondary">Apoyo a la Regularización</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ==============================
       Stats bar
       ============================== -->
  <section class="stats-bar">
    <div class="stats-inner">
      <div class="stat">
        <span class="stat-number">45+</span>
        <span class="stat-label">Años de historia</span>
      </div>
      <div class="stat">
        <span class="stat-number">30+</span>
        <span class="stat-label">Voluntarios activos</span>
      </div>
      <div class="stat">
        <span class="stat-number">7</span>
        <span class="stat-label">Proyectos activos</span>
      </div>
      <div class="stat">
        <span class="stat-number">100+</span>
        <span class="stat-label">Personas atendidas</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ==============================
       About
       ============================== -->
  <section class="section-about">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="about-grid">
        <div class="about-text">
          <span class="section-label">¿Quiénes somos?</span>
          <h2>Trabajamos por un barrio más justo</h2>
          <p>
            Somos una asociación sin ánimo de lucro que, desde 1977, promueve el desarrollo personal y comunitario
            de los vecinos y vecinas del Zaidín a través de la intervención socioeducativa.
          </p>
          <p>
            Actuamos sobre la realidad social del barrio con una mirada humana, participativa y transformadora.
            Creemos en el poder de la educación, la convivencia y la organización comunitaria para generar cambios reales.
          </p>
          <a href="/nuestra-historia/" class="btn btn-primary">Conoce nuestra historia →</a>
        </div>
        <div class="about-stats-cards">
          <div class="about-card card-mission">
            <span class="about-card-icon">🎯</span>
            <h3>Misión</h3>
            <p>Promover el desarrollo personal y comunitario desde la intervención socioeducativa.</p>
            <a href="/mision/" class="about-card-link">Leer más →</a>
          </div>
          <div class="about-card card-vision">
            <span class="about-card-icon">👁️</span>
            <h3>Visión</h3>
            <p>Ser un espacio de referencia, abierto y participativo para todo el barrio.</p>
            <a href="/vision/" class="about-card-link">Leer más →</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ==============================
       Values
       ============================== -->
  <section class="section-values">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <span class="section-label light">Nuestra esencia</span>
        <h2>Nuestros valores</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="values-grid">
        <div class="value-card">
          <div class="value-icon">⚖️</div>
          <div>
            <h3>Justicia Social</h3>
            <p>Solidaridad y ayuda mutua como base de nuestra acción comunitaria.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card">
          <div class="value-icon">🌍</div>
          <div>
            <h3>Convivencia Intercultural</h3>
            <p>La diversidad como riqueza. Respeto y diálogo entre culturas.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card">
          <div class="value-icon">🤝</div>
          <div>
            <h3>Participación Social</h3>
            <p>El barrio se construye desde abajo, con la implicación de cada persona.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card">
          <div class="value-icon">✊</div>
          <div>
            <h3>Igualdad de Género</h3>
            <p>Empoderamiento de las mujeres como motor de transformación social.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ==============================
       Projects
       ============================== -->
  <section class="section-projects">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <span class="section-label">Qué hacemos</span>
        <h2>Nuestros proyectos</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="project-grid">
        <article class="project-card">
          <div class="project-card-top">
            <span class="project-number">01</span>
            <span class="project-tag tag-educo">Infancia</span>
          </div>
          <h3>EDUCO</h3>
          <p>Voces de la Infancia Migrante — bienestar e inclusión de niños y adolescentes migrantes a través del arte y la comunidad.</p>
          <a href="/educo/" class="btn btn-primary">Saber más</a>
        </article>
        <article class="project-card">
          <div class="project-card-top">
            <span class="project-number">02</span>
            <span class="project-tag tag-educacion">Educación</span>
          </div>
          <h3>EDUCA ZAIDIN</h3>
          <p>Apoyo socioeducativo para familias y menores en riesgo de fracaso escolar. Refuerzo, orientación y acompañamiento.</p>
          <a href="/educa-zaidin/" class="btn btn-primary">Saber más</a>
        </article>
        <article class="project-card">
          <div class="project-card-top">
            <span class="project-number">03</span>
            <span class="project-tag tag-migracion">Migración</span>
          </div>
          <h3>TODOS SOMOS ZAIDIN</h3>
          <p>Clases de español, preparación de nacionalidad e integración social para vecinos de origen migrante.</p>
          <a href="/todos-somos-zaidin/" class="btn btn-primary">Saber más</a>
        </article>
        <article class="project-card">
          <div class="project-card-top">
            <span class="project-number">04</span>
            <span class="project-tag tag-igualdad">Igualdad</span>
          </div>
          <h3>FÓRMATE Y PARTICIPA</h3>
          <p>Talleres, cafés tertulia y acciones de sensibilización por la igualdad de género contra la violencia machista.</p>
          <a href="/formate-y-participa/" class="btn btn-primary">Saber más</a>
        </article>
      </div>
      <div class="projects-cta">
        <a href="/eracis/" class="btn btn-outline">Ver todos los proyectos →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ==============================
       Instagram
       ============================== -->
  <section class="section-instagram">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <span class="section-label light">Síguenos</span>
        <h2>Últimas publicaciones</h2>
      </div>
      <p class="instagram-subtitle">
        Síguenos en <a href="https://www.instagram.com/csc_zaidin/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">@csc_zaidin</a> para estar al día
      </p>
      <div class="instagram-grid">
        <a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/DXgl-C9iAuz/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="insta-card" style="background-image: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea, #764ba2);">
          <span class="insta-icon">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><rect x="2" y="2" width="20" height="20" rx="5"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="5"/><circle cx="17.5" cy="6.5" r="1.5"/></svg>
          </span>
          <span class="insta-label">Ver en Instagram</span>
        </a>
        <a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/DXbilpsiBKl/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="insta-card" style="background-image: linear-gradient(135deg, #f093fb, #f5576c);">
          <span class="insta-icon">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><rect x="2" y="2" width="20" height="20" rx="5"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="5"/><circle cx="17.5" cy="6.5" r="1.5"/></svg>
          </span>
          <span class="insta-label">Ver en Instagram</span>
        </a>
        <a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/DXMebG1CLES/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="insta-card" style="background-image: linear-gradient(135deg, #4facfe, #00f2fe);">
          <span class="insta-icon">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><rect x="2" y="2" width="20" height="20" rx="5"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="5"/><circle cx="17.5" cy="6.5" r="1.5"/></svg>
          </span>
          <span class="insta-label">Ver en Instagram</span>
        </a>
        <a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/DXEz8aYiFbP/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="insta-card" style="background-image: linear-gradient(135deg, #a18cd1, #fbc2eb);">
          <span class="insta-icon">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><rect x="2" y="2" width="20" height="20" rx="5"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="5"/><circle cx="17.5" cy="6.5" r="1.5"/></svg>
          </span>
          <span class="insta-label">Ver en Instagram</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ==============================
       CTA
       ============================== -->
  <section class="section-cta">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cta-box">
        <div class="cta-content">
          <span class="section-label light">Colabora</span>
          <h2>¿Quieres sumarte?</h2>
          <p>Con tu apoyo seguimos construyendo un barrio más justo para todas y todos.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="cta-buttons">
          <a href="/donaciones/" class="btn btn-cta-primary">❤️ Haz una donación</a>
          <a href="/colaboradores/" class="btn btn-cta-secondary">🧑‍🤝‍🧑 Hazte voluntario</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ==============================
       Regularization banner
       ============================== -->
  <section class="section-regularization">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="reg-banner">
        <div class="reg-icon">🇪🇸</div>
        <div class="reg-text">
          <h3>¿Necesitas el Informe de Vulnerabilidad para la Regularización Extraordinaria?</h3>
          <p>Te ayudamos con el proceso. Solicita cita por WhatsApp.</p>
        </div>
        <a href="/apoyo-a-la-regularizacion/" class="btn btn-primary">Más información</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style is:global>
  /* ==========================================================================
     Layout helpers
     ========================================================================== */
  .container {
    max-width: var(--max-w);
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 1.5rem;
  }

  .section-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .section-label {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    color: var(--teal-600);
    background: var(--teal-50);
    padding: 0.3rem 1rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }
  .section-label.light {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
    color: white;
  }

  .section-header h2 {
    font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 3vw, 2.2rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--text);
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  /* ==========================================================================
     Hero
     ========================================================================== */
  .hero {
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    min-height: 80vh;
    padding: 6rem 1.5rem;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .hero-bg {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background:
      linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(6,78,59,0.93) 0%, rgba(5,150,105,0.85) 50%, rgba(4,120,87,0.9) 100%),
      url('/images/cropped-header.jpg');
    background-size: cover;
    background-position: center;
    z-index: 0;
  }

  .hero-bg::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg width='60' height='60' viewBox='0 0 60 60' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cg fill='none' fill-rule='evenodd'%3E%3Cg fill='%23ffffff' fill-opacity='0.04'%3E%3Cpath d='M36 34v-4h-2v4h-4v2h4v4h2v-4h4v-2h-4zm0-30V0h-2v4h-4v2h4v4h2V6h4V4h-4zM6 34v-4H4v4H0v2h4v4h2v-4h4v-2H6zM6 4V0H4v4H0v2h4v4h2V6h4V4H6z'/%3E%3C/g%3E%3C/g%3E%3C/svg%3E");
    z-index: 0;
  }

  .hero-content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 780px;
    color: white;
  }

  .hero-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
    backdrop-filter: blur(4px);
    padding: 0.4rem 1.2rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
  }

  .hero-content h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 5.5vw, 3.5rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    text-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
  }

  .hero-tagline {
    font-size: clamp(0.95rem, 2vw, 1.2rem);
    font-weight: 300;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    opacity: 0.85;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .hero-quote {
    font-family: var(--font);
    font-size: clamp(0.95rem, 1.5vw, 1.1rem);
    line-height: 1.7;
    opacity: 0.92;
    padding: 1.5rem 2rem;
    border-left: 3px solid var(--warm-400);
    background: rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
    backdrop-filter: blur(4px);
    border-radius: 0 var(--radius-sm) var(--radius-sm) 0;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    text-align: left;
  }
  .hero-quote cite {
    display: block;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
    font-style: normal;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--warm-400);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .hero-actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .btn-hero-primary {
    padding: 0.8rem 2rem;
    background: white;
    color: var(--teal-700);
    font-weight: 700;
    border-radius: 999px;
    font-size: 1rem;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
    transition: transform var(--transition), box-shadow var(--transition);
  }
  .btn-hero-primary:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
    color: var(--teal-700);
  }

  .btn-hero-secondary {
    padding: 0.8rem 2rem;
    background: transparent;
    color: white;
    font-weight: 600;
    border-radius: 999px;
    font-size: 1rem;
    border: 2px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
    transition: background var(--transition), border-color var(--transition);
  }
  .btn-hero-secondary:hover {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    border-color: white;
    color: white;
  }

  /* ==========================================================================
     Stats bar
     ========================================================================== */
  .stats-bar {
    background: var(--bg);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .stats-inner {
    max-width: var(--max-w);
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 1px;
    background: var(--border);
  }
  .stat {
    background: var(--bg);
    padding: 2rem 1rem;
    text-align: center;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .stat-number {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--teal-600);
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }
  .stat-label {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  /* ==========================================================================
     About section
     ========================================================================== */
  .section-about {
    padding: 5rem 0;
    background: var(--bg);
  }
  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: start;
  }
  .about-text {
    padding-top: 1rem;
  }
  .about-text h2 {
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 2.5vw, 2rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--text);
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }
  .about-text p {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .about-stats-cards {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
  }
  .about-card {
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    transition: box-shadow var(--transition), transform var(--transition);
  }
  .about-card:hover {
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }
  .about-card-icon {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    display: block;
  }
  .about-card h3 {
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
    color: var(--text);
  }
  .about-card p {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }
  .about-card-link {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--teal-600);
  }
  .card-mission { border-left: 3px solid var(--teal-500); }
  .card-vision { border-left: 3px solid var(--warm-500); }

  /* ==========================================================================
     Values
     ========================================================================== */
  .section-values {
    padding: 5rem 0;
    background: var(--teal-800);
    color: white;
  }
  .section-values .section-header h2 { color: white; }

  .values-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 1rem;
  }
  .value-card {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 1rem;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    transition: background var(--transition), transform var(--transition);
  }
  .value-card:hover {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }
  .value-icon {
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
  }
  .value-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
    color: white;
  }
  .value-card p {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    opacity: 0.8;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  /* ==========================================================================
     Projects
     ========================================================================== */
  .section-projects {
    padding: 5rem 0;
    background: var(--bg-alt);
  }
  .project-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }
  .project-card {
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    transition: box-shadow var(--transition), transform var(--transition);
  }
  .project-card:hover {
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
    transform: translateY(-3px);
  }
  .project-card-top {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .project-number {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--teal-400);
  }
  .project-tag {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    padding: 0.2rem 0.7rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
    color: white;
  }
  .tag-educo { background: #764ba2; }
  .tag-educacion { background: #f093fb; }
  .tag-migracion { background: #4facfe; }
  .tag-igualdad { background: #f5576c; }

  .project-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .project-card p {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .projects-cta {
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
  }

  /* ==========================================================================
     Instagram
     ========================================================================== */
  .section-instagram {
    padding: 5rem 0;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--teal-800), #0f172a);
    color: white;
  }
  .section-instagram .section-header h2 { color: white; }
  .instagram-subtitle {
    text-align: center;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    margin-top: -2rem;
  }
  .instagram-subtitle a { color: var(--teal-300); }

  .instagram-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(200px, 1fr));
    gap: 1rem;
  }
  .insta-card {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    padding: 2rem 1rem;
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    text-decoration: none;
    color: white;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
    aspect-ratio: 1;
    transition: transform var(--transition), box-shadow var(--transition);
    text-align: center;
  }
